Usage: lunchtoast <test-path> [params] [flags] 
Arguments:
    <test-path> (path)     
Parameters:
   -r, --report <path>     save test report to file
                             (optional, default: "")
   -e, --ext <string>      the extension of searched test files, required when
                             specified test path is a directory
                             (optional, default: .toast)
   -w, --width <int>       set test report's width in number of characters
                             (optional, default: 48)
Flags:
   -s, --save-state        generate cleanup whitelist with content
                             of the test directory
       --help              show usage info and exit

